    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Underlod </strong>is an fast-paced arcade RTS. Build out your troops, and pilot them to victory. Inspired by classic RTS gameplay, along with elements from Diablo, Hearthstone, Dota, and auto-battlers. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Your troops attack automatically</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Move your units with the mouse to kite and dodge incoming attacks</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Choose troops during the run</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Buy powerful items to charge up your build</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 60+ passive items, with synergies to explore</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 3 different troops, each with a unique attack </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 3 difficulties plus endless mode</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 30+ Steam achievements</p></li></ul>",
